<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$qu-lin-8" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/qu-lin-8" class="zg-link" title="Shirley">Shirley</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xia-gua-teng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xia-gua-teng" class="zg-link" title="夏瓜藤">夏瓜藤</a></span>
